[SN]TITLE[SN]
General election 2017: How do people vote in an election?

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
There's not long left until the general election, when adults across the UK will decide who they want to run the country.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
26 May 2017 Last updated at 13:28 BST
The big vote on 8 June will reveal who runs the UK government  and who moves into 10 Downing Street as prime minister.
So voting's pretty important! But how does it happen?
Watch Whitney's report to find out.
